overview.en: GoWithMi is building a complete Decentralized Location Based Services (DLBS) infrastructure. It aims to provide a complete geospatial value exchange service for large-scale distributed commerce from data, computing, personal terminal to commercial ecological. GoWithMi's geospatial consensus ecological network consists of geospatial consensus data production, decentralized near-field cooperative computing network, self-organizing geospatial asset node, and business application sharing support platform. Integrated Decentralized Location Based Service (DLBS),super oracle, and consensus map platform, based on the algorithm consensus to motivate participation and achieve benefit for everyone, support all blockchain platforms through cross-chain technology and actively promote the application of blockchain in the real economy。
overview.zh: GoWithMi（高维地球）正在构建一个完整的去中心化位置服务基础设施，旨在为大规模分布式商业提供从数据端、计算端、个人终端到生态端的完整的空间价值交换服务。GoWithMi的空间共识价值生态网络由空间共识数据源生产、去中心化近场协同计算网络、空间资产节点自组织和商业应用共享支持平台组成，集去中心化位置服务、超级预言机和共识地图于一体，基于算法共识激励人人参与、实现人人受益，通过跨链技术支持所有区块链平台，推动区块链落地实体经济。
